k Ostrava players]]\n[[Category:Liverpool F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Aston Villa F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Olympique Lyonnais players]]\n[[Category:Portsmouth F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Galatasaray S.K. footballers]]\n[[Category:Antalyaspor footballers]]\n[[Category:FK Mlad\u00e1 Boleslav players]]\n[[Category:FC Slovan Liberec players]]\n[[Category:Czech First League players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Champions League winning players]]\n[[Category:Czech Republic youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Czech Republic under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Olympic footballers of the Czech Republic]]\n[[Category:Czech Republic international footballers]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 2000 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2004 players]]\n[[Category:2006 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2008 players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2012 players]]\n[[Category:Czech expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Czech expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Czech expatriate sportspeople in France]]\n[[Category:Czech expatriate sportspeople in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in France]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n", "text_old": "{{good article}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Milan Baro\u0161\n| image = Milan Baro\u01613, FCB-SLAVIA 30092018.jpg\n| alt = Photograph of a player in a white football kit standing on grass\n| image_size = 240\n| caption = Baro\u0161 with [[Ban\u00edk Ostrava]] in 2018\n| fullname = Milan Baro\u0161<ref name=\"Hugman2008-09\">{{Cite book\n | editor-first = Barry J.\n | editor-last = Hugman\n | title = The PFA Footballers' Who's Who 2008\u201309\n | year = 2008\n | publisher = Mainstream Publishing\n | isbn = 978-1-84596-324-8\n | page = 38 }}</ref>\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1981|10|28}}<ref name=\"Hugman2008-09\"/>\n| 