rk=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=11 August 2002 |accessdate=23 July 2013}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Milan Baro\u0161}}\n* [http://www.lfchistory.net/Players/Player/Profile/263 Profile] at LFChistory.net\n* {{TFF player|1172360}}\n* {{FIFA player|177896}}\n* {{NFT player|id=1826}}\n* {{Soccerbase}}\n* [http://en.fortunaliga.cz/hrac/921-milan-baros Milan Baro\u0161] Official Czech First League statistics\n* {{Fotbal DNES|id=3000263}}\n\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title= Czech Republic squads\n|bg= #D7141A\n|fg= white\n|bordercolor=#11457E\n|list1=\n{{Czech Republic men's football squad 2000 Summer Olympics}}\n{{Czech Republic squad UEFA Euro 2004}}\n{{Czech Republic squad 2006 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Czech Republic squad UEFA Euro 2008}}\n{{Czech Republic squad UEFA Euro 2012}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|bg=gold\n|fg=navy\n|title= Awards\n|list1=\n{{Czech Talent of the Year}}\n{{UEFA European Football Championship top scorers}}\n{{Turkish Super League topscorers}}\n{{UEFA Euro 2004 Team of the Tournament}}\n{{100 players who shook the Kop}}\n}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2013}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Baros, Milan}}\n[[Category:1981 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Vala\u0161sk\u00e9 Mezi\u0159\u00ed\u010d\u00ed]]\n[[Category:Czech footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:FC Ban\u00edk Ostrava players]]\n[[Category:Liverpool F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Aston Villa F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Olympique Lyonnais players]]\n[[Category:Portsmouth F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Galatasaray S.K. footballers]]\n[[Category:Antalyaspor footballers]]\n[[Category:FK Mlad\u00e1 Boleslav players]]\n[[Category:FC Slovan Liberec players]]\n[[Category:Czech First League players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Champions League winning play