 Tompkins]]&nbsp;\u2013 U.S. Vice President, born in [[Westchester County, New York|Westchester County]]\n*[[Frederick Trump]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[German American]] businessman\n*[[Melania Trump]]&nbsp;\u2013 45th [[First Lady of the United States]] and model, born in [[Slovenia]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n=== U ===\n*[[Johannes Urzidil]]&nbsp;\u2013 writer, born in [[Prague]], [[Bohemia]]\n\n=== V ===\n{{div col}}\n*[[Martin Van Buren]]&nbsp;\u2013 U.S. President, born in [[Kinderhook, New York]]\n*[[Andrew VanWyngarden]]{{spaced ndash}}member of [[MGMT]]\n*[[Gary Vaynerchuk]]{{spaced ndash}} serial entrepreneur and best-selling author\n*[[Jon Voight]]&nbsp;\u2013 actor, born in [[Yonkers, New York]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n=== W ===\n{{div col}}\n*[[Rufus Wainwright]]{{spaced ndash}}musician, born in [[Rhinebeck (town), New York|Rhinebeck]], New York\n*[[John Evangelist Walsh]]&nbsp;\u2013 writer and historian, editor of the [[Reader's Digest Bible]]\n*[[Barbara Walters]]&nbsp;\u2013 TV journalist and personality, born in [[Boston]]\n*[[Dean Wareham]]&nbsp;\u2013 singer-songwriter, born in New Zealand\n*[[Andy Warhol]]&nbsp;\u2013 artist, born in [[Pittsburgh]]\n*[[Denzel Washington]]&nbsp;\u2013 actor, born in [[Mount Vernon, New York]]\n*[[Walt Whitman]]&nbsp;\u2013 poet and author, born in [[West Hills, New York|West Hills]] ([[Long Island, New York|Long Island]]), New York\n*[[Olivia Wilde]]&nbsp;\u2013 actress\n*[[Barney Williams (actor)|Barney Williams]]{{spaced ndash}} Irish-American comedian\n*[[Jayson Williams]]&nbsp;\u2013 basketball player, born in Ritter, South Carolina\n*[[Christopher Woodrow]]&nbsp;\u2013 movie producer, born in [[Syracuse, New York]]\n*[[Jason Wu]] &ndash; fashion designer.\n{{div col end}}\n{{Columns-end}}\n\n== See also ==\n{{Portal|Biography|Lists|New York City}}\n*[[List of people from New York]]\n*By borough:\n**[[List of people from the Bronx]]\n**[[List of people from Brooklyn]]\n**[[List of people from Manhattan]]\n***[[List of people from 